title: Banyan Live (mp3) 2002-Feb-19, Bozeman, MT
description:
Sick concert i attended a few years ago at the Zebra Cocktail Lounge in Bozeman, MT. Place was a lot darker then, than it is now - crowd of about 150ppl jammed in this tiny joint. Smoky and hot and gnarly, this concert scared the living shit out of me. i\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&#039;ve seen banyan several times since and they\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&#039;re always extremely exciting; this moment in time, though... bad-ass. hope you like. go to their concerts. buy their stuff. they pay serious dues. plz be patient with my limited seeding ability, i\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&#039;ll be on at least every day for a few hours, usually daytime mountain time.

Featuring:
Stephen Perkins: drums
Willie Waldman: trumpet
Mike Watt: bass
Nels Cline: guitar

enjoy...
